1. What are streams?
 : - Stream API is new feature available form java 8. By using stream we can perform various aggregate oprations on the data returned
 form collection classes by reduce the complexity of code.
 
2. Lambda Expression (->)
 - It divides the lambda expression into tow parts:
   - the left side specifies the parameter required by the expression which could also be empty.
   - the right side is the lambda body which specifies the actions of lambda expression.